# List locale codes {% #list-locale-codes %}

You can also retrieve a list of all available locale codes:

{% multicode %}
```client-web
const localeCodes = await locale.listCodes();

console.log(localeCodes);
// {
//   total: 100+,
//   codes: ['en', 'es', 'fr', 'de', ...]
// }
```
```client-flutter
Future result = locale.listCodes().then((response) {
    print(response.total);
    print(response.codes);
    return response;
}).catchError((error) {
    print(error.response);
});
```
```client-apple
let localeCodes = try await locale.listCodes()

print(localeCodes.total)
print(localeCodes.codes)
```
```client-android-kotlin
val localeCodes = locale.listCodes()

println(localeCodes.total)
println(localeCodes.codes)
```
```client-react-native
